high_descs: Move to the stove so you are facing it.
Pick up the glass to the left of the stove.
Walk to the fridge and face it.
Open the fridge and put the glass on the left side of the middle shelf and close the door and let it sit and chill before retrieving it and closing the fridge door again.
Turn right and walk to the sink and face it.
Put the glass in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled glass in the sink.

high_descs: Go straight ahead and to the left until you're to the left of the stove.
Pick up the glass.
Turn left and walk to the fridge.
Put the glass in the fridge. Close the door, wait a moment, and then take it out again.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Place the cup in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled cup in the sink.

high_descs: Turn slightly left and move forward toward the stove.
Pick up the glass on the back of the counter, left of the stove.
Hold the glass and move a few steps left to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the glass inside. Shut the door then open it. Get the glass out and shut the door.
Take the glass and turn around to find the sink.
Place the glass inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Chill a glass then place it in the sink.

high_descs: Walk to the counter in front of you then take two steps left.
Pick up the cup to the left of the stove.
Turn left and walk to the fridge and when you get to it turn right to face it.
Chill the glass in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the stove then turn right and walk to the sink.
Put the glass in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold glass in the sink.

high_descs: Turn left towards the glass cup on the counter.
Pick up the cup from the counter.
Turn left towards the fridge and face the fridge.
Place the cup next to the bowl in the fridge and remove the cup from the fridge after a moment.
Turn around and walk towards the sink.
Place the cup inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the glass cup from the counter to the sink.

high_descs: Turn and go to the counter that is to the left of the stove.
Pick up the cup that is on the back of the counter and next to the stove.
With the cup in hand turn and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and place the cup on the third shelf down to the left of cucumber.  Close the fridge.  Open the fridge and grab the cup on the third shelf.
With the cup in hand turn and go to the sink.
Place the cup in the middle of the sink.
